data.description: This charming home is perfect for a small family or couple.  It features two bedrooms, a full bathroom and a cozy living room. The kitchen has a new LG refrigerator as well as a new farmhouse sink with a pull-out faucet.  The bathroom has also been updated plus a new Whilpool dryer in the laundry room. Out back you will find a small storage building for all your things plus a small patio to do all your grilling on. This one is definitely worth the look. Call us for a showing!
